FLOODING POPPY PLAYTIME IN WATER!!! (Can Huggy Swim?) | Poppy Playtime Gameplay (Mods)

What’s up MA DUDES!!!! How is it going today? Today we are going to be playing Poppy Playtime with the WATER FLOOD MOD!!! We are flooding the entire map of Poppy Playtime and Huggy Wuggy is going to have to learn how to swim!!! In this episode we are filling everything up with water and Huggy Wuggy goes crazy! With these mods, we can do anything we want and my buddy Kokosko has made it so that we can use hacks in Poppy Playtime, fly in Poppy Playtime, noclip in Poppy Playtime, and even prepare for Poppy Playtime Chapter 2! In our last mods we made Huggy Wuggy friendly, we made Huggy Wuggy Tiny and now we are making Huggy Wuggy Swim in Water! Let’s break the game and play it differently as we hack Poppy Playtime and add mods to FLOOD EVERYTHING IN WATER!!! Enjoy
